Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:35.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:40.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:47.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:52.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:57.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:11.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:14.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:23.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:26.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:38.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:35.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜歡著緊張的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:40.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}興奮起來走向更廣闊的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:47.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:52.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只專注於眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:57.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰都無法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前進的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}連同那份淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部開始閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:11.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此將宿於手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:14.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}盡情揮揚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果斷地  徑直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向著明天全力進發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:23.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在轉瞬即逝之間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:26.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}實現那夢中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}無論它多麼虛幻和遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和僅屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:38.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹劍節奏響徹永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第24話\N劍與道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼想要退部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說點什麼嘛  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫不上大家的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前不是說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為小珠你的加入  劍道部才越來越好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次也還是輸掉比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸掉比賽不光是小珠的錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是因為我不得不勝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不得不勝  所以不可以輸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那場大賽上我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我強的人有很多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫不上大家的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道還有什麼繼續劍道的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這樣說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你再也不參加活動也好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒交給老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學也沒有來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去教室的時候已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先開始練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫老師過來  你們就先去練擺振吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君  宮崎同學說了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我派不上用場嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！從勇次君開始連續30次  喊出聲來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  也不能強拉她回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底  部團活動參加與否還是要遵從個人意識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  今天我有點事情  不能去道場了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山他們的事情明天做個決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要逃避問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是顧問嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  辛苦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…老師他都說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個顧問腦子在想什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是劍道部最大危機呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  總會有辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要考慮考慮那些一年級的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是顧問嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的劍道  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天都不碰竹劍  有幾年沒這麼做了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子火焰劍！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為這樣就結束了  Blade Braver！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管幾次我都會復活的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼不管幾次我都保護給你看！人們的笑容！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…前輩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天向學校請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想倒也不會是那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會一起去探病吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也不在家裡  手機也不接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是不是讓她靜靜比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃那邊我回去時再過去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…紀梨乃前輩最近是不是有點怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒那回事喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  別在意小事  來練習來練習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師今天也不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好冷清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過原來就不算熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（無他）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆胎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本不用陪我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  你不再練劍道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也說用不著刻意去練
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都是刻意在練嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你有沒有想過想要讓自己的劍道變得更強？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有想過想贏過那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠以前問過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸掉的時候是什麼樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那一定就是小珠現在感受到的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  小珠你輸給她  輸給凜所以很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你以前一直都比別人強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在面對這份不甘心不知道如何是好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸掉…原來是這樣子的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用不著放棄啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道早已把今後的道路準備完全了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那份不甘心為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力並最終取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與不甘心比起來還有遠勝於它的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力並取勝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小珠不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為輸了很多次所以明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白這點之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會喜歡上劍道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來動起來  安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  突然找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  有件事情請您務必告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您教我與上段對戰的方法吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要打贏她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  看來終於開竅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊  你們那邊不就有個打上段的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了  老師用上段打贏過石橋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您了  請教我和上段對戰的方法吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被逼急了亂打上去的一劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不會打什麼上段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您了  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有什麼可教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本來就強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常練劍道的話  總有一日會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會出現一定打不贏的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係  部團活動這種東西只要高興就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想忘記今天察覺的這份不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於開始了…自己的劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要面對自己的失敗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來！石田！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道不好好面對就談不上開始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:12:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去道場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從城裡騎自行車一直過來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是明天再開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  大家都在擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  別跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和段君之間發生什麼事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是凱莉的事情的話不早就過去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是二刀流  只要努力練習超過她不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎和你怎麼會明白我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要對方跟我一樣努力練習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她的差距就永遠不會縮小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有可能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一味地陷在對方的話裡面這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是凱莉她元旦啊盂盆節啊聖誕節也會休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差距絕對可以縮小的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上她要花多少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果努力也都是白費的話  練劍道還有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要胡說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰能說努力都是白費  誰敢這麼說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒有這樣想過！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是輸了兩次就想放棄  想消沉  想逃避的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒資格這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想放棄的話就給我贏了再放棄啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別糟蹋了我的特訓！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你不想活了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我做好準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從頭開始鍛煉直到我打倒你為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃  我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了  你突然跑來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是你請假不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小鞘…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想什麼？連你都想退出嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想這樣校長就能網開一面…責任讓部長來承擔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在能做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼總是這樣笨呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難過也好痛苦也好總是笑眯眯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把一切都攬到自己頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這樣煩惱就能解決了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭有什麼關係！難過有什麼關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我不就可以來幫你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人煩心什麼都做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果齊心協力能解決問題的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來找我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自決定啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的想這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…也會跟著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就能下決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊啦  今天會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我有鼓勵小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際上我是不是根本不理解她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有什麼非贏不可的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我還是只能嘴上說說加油嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事…段君你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  只有男生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛你們  還不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休部？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？下次再來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩  等等再說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來打發下時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後大鬧一場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我打  一年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退後  勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不討厭劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不相信  他也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  一年級！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  不適合我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道到最後都這麼無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個交給紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日期是春天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們和部團就沒什麼關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也不能強行休部了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是騙人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上就是在那之後寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠那個笨蛋的人情算是還清了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是部長做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直放在更衣室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝指導
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣多少能理解一點小都都的感受了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問問她如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣前輩們也比較高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳  我們部什麼時候開始這麼熱鬧了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  作為部長我不想讓大家太擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  雖說是部長但也是部員嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就是他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出午時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒勞得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}閉上眼睛傾聽心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然無法得知  它想與我相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光輝而耀眼的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.59,0:23:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  下回的竹劍少女是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呀  第25話  「劍道和劍道所帶來的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:23:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有2話就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這期間小都都會贏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的黑化不管怎麼看都還可愛呀  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～段郎  你那大海一般的胸懷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人真是太棒啦可惡耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  你這個任性的小朱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道給他們帶來了什麼啊…
